    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新内容计划在 11 月 2 日更新，包含： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法工艺联动人格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个新的关卡、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7个收费的武器皮肤 DLC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入我们的社区</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ群: 812627126(满了)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ群: 13305571(没满)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>B站：丸霸于大进BigYu</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抖音：丸霸于大进BigYu</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器好几种</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前提供了5种武器可供使用，它们分别是，弓，枪，炮，斧，琴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/e5252f58ac249c69098c589aaa51b2d0.poster.avif?t=1730479980\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/e5252f58ac249c69098c589aaa51b2d0.webm?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/e5252f58ac249c69098c589aaa51b2d0.mp4?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大坐快乐多</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄游中独特的、快节奏的、大坐系统，越坐越快乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/9d3bfcff2e6ef3f9f9341bcdaea97b6c.poster.avif?t=1730479980\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/9d3bfcff2e6ef3f9f9341bcdaea97b6c.webm?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/9d3bfcff2e6ef3f9f9341bcdaea97b6c.mp4?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成长很丰富</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中有大量的道具和技能，通过不同的搭配，形成不同的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/c91e14718c68634d21e0db90c91c80c3.poster.avif?t=1730479980\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/c91e14718c68634d21e0db90c91c80c3.webm?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/c91e14718c68634d21e0db90c91c80c3.mp4?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人炸了窝</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的场景，会遭遇不同的敌人，它们形态各异，性格多样，劈里啪啦，咔咔冒水。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/f9599d6c4a1fd8f72acbfdfaae9c0843.poster.avif?t=1730479980\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/f9599d6c4a1fd8f72acbfdfaae9c0843.webm?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/f9599d6c4a1fd8f72acbfdfaae9c0843.mp4?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3A级游戏体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然这只是一个小团队的独立游戏，但我们希望营造出3A级的游戏体验，而令人愉快的是，我们做到了，我们成功的修改了3A的定义：A LOT OF 饼；A LOT OF 钱；A LOT OF 鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/0bfd003229e3d86d13e4053621ae5a6e.poster.avif?t=1730479980\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/0bfd003229e3d86d13e4053621ae5a6e.webm?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710100/extras/0bfd003229e3d86d13e4053621ae5a6e.mp4?t=1730479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
